---
import Landing from '@/layout/Landing.astro';
---

<Landing 
    title="Privacy Policy" 
    description="Learn how Anyclazz collects, processes, and protects your personal data in compliance with GDPR and CCPA."
    keywords={['privacy', 'data protection', 'GDPR', 'CCPA', 'personal data']}
>
    <section class="px-4 pt-32 pb-20">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center mb-16">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-primary-700)] mb-3">Legal</p>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-500 max-w-[50ch]">Learn how Anyclazz collects, processes, and protects your personal data.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">1. Data Controller</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    Anyclazz S.L. ("Anyclazz") is the data controller responsible for processing personal data.
                </p>
                <ul class="list-none space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li><strong>Company ID:</strong> B-22956890</li>
                    <li><strong>Address:</strong> Calle Calvo Sotelo 7, Madrid, Spain</li>
                    <li><strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@anyclazz.com" class="text-[var(--color-primary-600)] hover:underline">info@anyclazz.com</a></li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">2. Categories of Personal Data</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    Depending on your use of the platform, we may collect the following categories of data:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li><strong>Identifiers:</strong> name, email, login credentials</li>
                    <li><strong>Commercial data:</strong> bookings, transactions, payment metadata</li>
                    <li><strong>Internet activity:</strong> IP address, browsing interactions</li>
                    <li><strong>Device data:</strong> browser, operating system</li>
                    <li><strong>User content:</strong> profiles, descriptions, videos</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">3. Sources of Data</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    We collect data directly from users, automatically through platform usage, and from third-party
                    service providers such as payment processors.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">4. Purposes of Processing</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    We process data to operate the platform, enable bookings, process payments, improve services,
                    ensure security, and comply with legal obligations.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">5. Legal Bases (GDPR)</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">Processing is based on:</p>
                <ul class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li>Contractual necessity</li>
                    <li>Legal obligations</li>
                    <li>Legitimate interests (security, fraud prevention)</li>
                    <li>Consent (marketing, cookies where applicable)</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">6. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">We may disclose personal data to:</p>
                <ul class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li>Payment processors (e.g., Stripe)</li>
                    <li>Cloud hosting providers</li>
                    <li>Analytics providers</li>
                    <li>Legal authorities when required</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">7. No Sale or Sharing (CCPA)</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    Anyclazz does not sell or share personal data as defined under the California Consumer Privacy
                    Act (CCPA/CPRA).
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">8. International Data Transfers</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    Data may be transferred from the United States to the European Union and other jurisdictions.
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    Transfers are protected using Standard Contractual Clauses or equivalent safeguards.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">9. Data Retention</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    We retain personal data only as long as necessary for service provision, legal compliance, and
                    legitimate business purposes.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">10. Your Rights (GDPR & CCPA)</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">Users may exercise the following rights:</p>
                <ul class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li>Access and obtain a copy of data</li>
                    <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
                    <li>Request deletion of data</li>
                    <li>Restrict or object to processing</li>
                    <li>Data portability</li>
                    <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">11. California Privacy Rights</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">California residents have additional rights:</p>
                <ul class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li>Right to know categories and specific data collected</li>
                    <li>Right to request deletion</li>
                    <li>Right to request correction</li>
                    <li>Right to opt-out (not applicable as no sale occurs)</li>
                    <li>Right to non-discrimination</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">12. Exercising Your Rights</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    Requests may be submitted to <a href="mailto:info@anyclazz.com" class="text-[var(--color-primary-600)] hover:underline">info@anyclazz.com</a>.
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    We may verify identity before processing requests.
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    We respond within statutory timelines (e.g., 45 days under CCPA).
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">13. Marketing Communications</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">Marketing communications comply with the CAN-SPAM Act:</p>
                <ul class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li>Clear identification of sender</li>
                    <li>No misleading subject lines</li>
                    <li>Opt-out/unsubscribe mechanism included</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">14. Children's Privacy (COPPA)</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    The platform is not intended for children under 13.
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13.
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    If such data is identified, it will be deleted promptly.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">15. Data Security</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures including encryption, access
                    controls, and monitoring.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">16. Cookies</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    Cookies and tracking technologies are governed by the <a href="/legal/cookie-policy" class="text-[var(--color-primary-600)] hover:underline">Cookie Policy</a>.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">17. Changes to this Policy</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Continued use of the platform constitutes
                    acceptance of changes.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">18. Contact</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    For any privacy-related inquiries: <a href="mailto:info@anyclazz.com" class="text-[var(--color-primary-600)] hover:underline">info@anyclazz.com</a>
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Landing>
